Your Trusted Software Quality Assurance Consulting Company

Software QA consulting services help organize and fine-tune a QA workflow as well as remove complications within an existing QA process, leading to higher QA maturity and efficiency. Hashlogics assists businesses in promptly assessing their QA processes and ensuring their proficiency by implementing smart test automation, effectively testing specialized software types, and crafting a robust QA process right from scratch. With our vast experience spanning various fields, including Healthcare, FinTech, Real Estate, Cybersecurity, Retail, and ad tech, we passionately implement a unified approach and implement industry best practices when addressing complex solutions.

Book A Free Strategy Call

Software QA Consulting Services We Offer

QA Process Improvement

Hashlogics QA consultants identify and mitigate problems in your QA process, analyze risks, implement improvements, and evaluate effectiveness against agreed KPIs.

QA Process Setup

Our software QA consultants analyze software specifics, outline testing scope and strategy, estimate time and costs, and assess test automation feasibility before setting up the QA process.

QA Process Audit

Our expert quality assurance consultants examine current QA processes, identify bottlenecks, optimize processes, and provide action plans for improvement, including maturity assessments and upgrade recommendations if needed.

Pre-certification QA Aid

Our experts analyze business specifics, elicit compliance requirements, assess current practices, advise on improvements, and create roadmaps to compliance, including reassessment readiness for certification audits.

Test Automation Introduction

Hashlogics professionals analyze project specifics, conduct feasibility studies, design automation strategies, advise on tools and configurations, set up automated testing, and integrate continuous testing into CI/CD pipelines.

Consulting on Testing Software

Hashlogics engineers design test strategies and plans, outline testing scopes and approaches, advise on team lineup and competencies, and assess test automation feasibility for various application types, architectures, and technologies.

Quality Assurance Consulting Services To Optimize Your Business

Businesses need QA consulting services to ensure the quality of their software products and rationalize their development processes. A QA consultant can make recommendations for optimizing effectiveness, lowering expenses, and raising overall quality, as well as help identify areas for improvement in the companys QA practices. Here are four key reasons:
  • Expertise and Best Practices
  • Cost Efficiency
  • Improved Product Quality
  • Objective Assessment

When To Use Software Quality Assurance Consulting

Non-Efficient QA Process
Struggling with basic test coverage? Our QA consultation brings urgent action plans.
Structural Team Changes
QA consultancy ensures smooth role assignments and knowledge transfer among changes.
Poor Product Quality
Reverse declining software quality with QA consultants’ expertise.
Lack Of In-House Expertise
Fill competency gaps swiftly and cost-effectively with software QA consulting.
Unoptimized QA Procedures
Transform overwhelming workflows into superior-quality software with skilled software test consultants.
High Cost Of Testing
Balancing testing costs with benefits is critical. Consulting identifies and rectifies cost-related issues.

Software Testing Consulting Step by Step

Hashlogics consultants follow a comprehensive approach to software quality assurance consulting. Below are the key stages of our QA testing consulting services:

Initial Consultation

Discuss your needs and objectives to understand the project scope.

Discovery Phase

Evaluate processes, interview stakeholders, identify deficiencies, and establish project goals.

Assessment

Perform a detailed assessment of current QA practices and identify areas for improvement.

Project Planning

Define scope, assess risks, create a roadmap, and select tools for effective project management.

Strategy Development

Develop a customized QA strategy tailored to your specific needs and project goals.

Implementation

Collaborate with your team, execute the QA plan, supervise progress, and address any emerging issues promptly.

Post-Project Analysis

Evaluate outcomes, mitigate risks, develop action plans, and provide comprehensive test documentation for future reference.

Continuous Support & Maintenance

Offer ongoing improvement suggestions, monitor progress, assist with challenges, and provide holistic project support as needed.

FAQs

frequently asked questions

How long does a QA consulting engagement typically last?
The duration of a QA consulting engagement varies based on the scope and complexity of the project. It can range from a few weeks for a specific assessment to several months for comprehensive process improvement initiatives.
What is the cost of QA consulting services?
The cost varies based on the scope and complexity of the project. We offer flexible pricing models including hourly rates, fixed-price contracts, and dedicated QA teams. A detailed estimate is provided after understanding your specific requirements.
How do you ensure the quality of your QA consulting services?
We have a team of experienced QA consultants who follow industry best practices and methodologies. Our approach is tailored to your specific needs, ensuring high-quality recommendations and implementations.
Can you help with setting up a QA process from scratch?
Yes, we can help you establish a robust QA process from the ground up. This includes defining QA roles and responsibilities, selecting appropriate tools, creating test plans, and implementing best practices.
How do you handle QA process assessments?
We conduct thorough assessments of your existing QA processes, identifying gaps and areas for improvement. Based on the assessment, we provide actionable recommendations to enhance your QA efficiency and effectiveness.
What are the benefits of engaging your QA consultant?
Benefits include expert guidance, improved QA processes, reduced defects, faster time-to-market, enhanced product quality, and the ability to focus your in-house team on core development activities.
How do you handle communication and reporting during a QA consulting project?
We use collaborative tools like JIRA, Slack, Trello, and regular meetings to ensure clear communication and reporting. Detailed reports, progress updates, and regular reviews keep you informed throughout the consulting engagement.
How do you tailor your QA consulting services to our specific needs?
We start with a thorough understanding of your business objectives, existing QA processes, and challenges. Based on this, we develop customized strategies and recommendations to meet your specific needs and goals.
